{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusProxyRef\/onNotifyGInterfaceName(flags:handler:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyGInterfaceName"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" = ConnectFlags(0), "},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"DBusProxyRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusProxyRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO12DBusProxyRefV"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ParamSpecRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"flags","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Flags","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"handler","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Run the given callback whenever the ","type":"text"},{"code":"notifyGInterfaceName","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" signal is emitted","type":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"code":"g_object_notify()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_signal_connect()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This represents the underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify::g-interface-name"},{"type":"text","text":" signal"}]}],"style":"note","name":"Note","type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_set()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"extendedModule":"GIO","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyGInterfaceName"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"ConnectFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"text":": (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"DBusProxyRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO12DBusProxyRefV"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"}],"title":"onNotifyGInterfaceName(flags:handler:)","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"s:3GIO17DBusProxyProtocolPAAE22onNotifyGInterfaceName5flags7handlerSi10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV_yAA0bC3RefV_AG09ParamSpecO0VtctF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO12DBusProxyRefV","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"role":"symbol"